    CcddClassesDataTable

    public static class CcddClassesDataTable.AssociatedColumns

    Command argument class. Contains associated command argument name, data type, enumeration, minimum value, and maximum value column indices in view or model coordinates (as specified)

                            int name,

                            int minimum,
                            int maximum,
                            int description,
                            int units,
                            java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> other)
        Command argument class constructor for setting associated command argument columns
        Parameters:
        useViewIndex - true to adjust the column indices to view coordinates; false to keep the coordinates in model coordinates
        name - command argument name data type column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        dataType - command argument data type column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        arraySize - command argument array size column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        bitLength - command argument bit length column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        enumeration - command argument enumeration column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        minimum - command argument minimum value column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        maximum - command argument maximum value column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        description - command argument description column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        units - command argument units column index, model coordinates; -1 if none
        other - list of other associated column indices, model coordinates; null if none
